        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Guaranteeing Overtime for Truckers Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires employers of commercial truck drivers to provide overtime pay to such drivers engaged in a workweek longer than 40 hours.</p>]]>
        </text>
